{"id":106305,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/09/图辑：中国民众举行反日保钓示威/","date":"2010-09-21T08:56:11Z","modified":"2010-09-23T19:13:00Z","title":"图辑：中国民众举行反日保钓示威","content":"<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/09/18/100918054632_cndemo_01_afp_926x521_afp.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"北京反日民众在日本驻华大使馆外示威（18/9/2010）\" height=\"60\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x60/www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/09/18/100918054632_cndemo_01_afp_926x521_afp.jpg\" width=\"106\" /></a></div>\n<div>中国多个城市星期六（9月18日）有民众举行反日示威。抗议日本在有主权争议的钓鱼岛海域（日本称尖阁诸岛）拘留中国渔船船长。</div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/09/18/100918054948_cndemo_02_reuters_926x521_reuters.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"北京反日民众在日本驻华大使馆外喊口号（18/9/2010）\" height=\"60\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x60/www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/09/18/100918054948_cndemo_02_reuters_926x521_reuters.jpg\" width=\"106\" /></a></div>\n<div>示威者要求日本“滚出钓鱼岛”，高喊“打倒日本军国主义”，更有人喊“美国人滚出亚洲”。</div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/09/18/100918055157_cndemo_03_ap_417x521_ap.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"北京反日民众在日本大使馆外举起还我船长标语（18/9/2010）\" height=\"60\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x60/www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/09/18/100918055157_cndemo_03_ap_417x521_ap.jpg\" width=\"106\" /></a></div>\n<div>目前“闽晋渔5179”号船长詹其雄仍被扣押在冲绳，示威群众要求日方马上放人。</div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/09/18/100918055342_cndemo_04_ap_417x521_ap.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"北京反日民众在日本大使馆外践踏自制日本国旗（18/9/2010）\" height=\"60\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x60/www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/09/18/100918055342_cndemo_04_ap_417x521_ap.jpg\" width=\"106\" /></a></div>\n<div>一些示威群众践踏日本国旗泄愤。</div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/09/18/100918055640_cndemo_05_reuters_926x521_reuters.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"北京反日民众在日本大使馆外展示写有日本人滚出钓鱼岛的蛋糕（18/9/2010）\" height=\"60\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x60/www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/09/18/100918055640_cndemo_05_reuters_926x521_reuters.jpg\" width=\"106\" /></a></div>\n<div>也有示威者用另类方式来表达不满：这个写有“日本人滚出钓鱼岛”的蛋糕上，画上了钓鱼岛插上中国国旗的图案。</div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/09/18/100918060528_cndemo_06_afp_926x521_afp.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"北京反日民众游行至使馆区时警员试图劝离（18/9/2010）\" height=\"60\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x60/www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/09/18/100918060528_cndemo_06_afp_926x521_afp.jpg\" width=\"106\" /></a></div>\n<div>中国各地警方严阵以待，设法劝导示威群众离开。</div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/09/18/100918060722_cndemo_07_ap_926x521_ap.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"北京日本驻华大使馆外武警封锁馆外街道（18/9/2010）\" height=\"60\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x60/www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/09/18/100918060722_cndemo_07_ap_926x521_ap.jpg\" width=\"106\" /></a></div>\n<div>在北京，武警人员后来把通往日本大使馆的道路封锁，禁止民众靠近。</div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/09/18/100918060924_cndemo_08_rthk_626x470_rthk.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"广东深圳反日示威者欲前往日资百货公司抗议被警方阻止（香港电台图片18/9/2010）\" height=\"60\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x60/www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/09/18/100918060924_cndemo_08_rthk_626x470_rthk.jpg\" width=\"106\" /></a></div>\n<div>在广东深圳，示威者希望前往日资百货公司抗议，也被警员阻止前进。</div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><a href=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/09/18/100918061126_cndemo_09_reuters_926x521_reuters.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"上海反日示威者展示的中国国旗（18/9/2010）\" height=\"60\" src=\"http://wscdn.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/ic/106x60/www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/assets/images/2010/09/18/100918061126_cndemo_09_reuters_926x521_reuters.jpg\" width=\"106\" /></a></div>\n<div>中国官方采取了强硬态度与日方就撞船事件进行交涉，但此间分析认为，当局担心反日怒潮最终反而危及中国社会稳定。</div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</li>\n</ul></div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/LzddsF3EmY4ze7wTN15D9spLZv8/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/LzddsF3EmY4ze7wTN15D9spLZv8/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/LzddsF3EmY4ze7wTN15D9spLZv8/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/LzddsF3EmY4ze7wTN15D9spLZv8/1/di\"></a></p>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/BBC/China/~4/v5fMXRA8rmI\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p>请看原文：<br />\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/china/2010/09/100918_gal_china_japan_protest.shtml\" title=\"图辑：中国民众举行反日保钓示威\">图辑：中国民众举行反日保钓示威</a></p>\n","author":138,"categories":[8779],"tags":[14208]}